--- RESULT ---
Both pages are built and the build succeeded — **1420 pages built in 36.91s**.

### Product Detail Page (`src/pages/product/[slug].astro`)
- `getStaticPaths()` generates 1412 pages from `data/products.json`
- **Breadcrumb**: Home > Category > Brand > Product Name
- **Hero section**: 2-column layout with product image (with fallback), brand badge, product name, category/release date, RatingBadge, price display, and Compare button
- **Quick Specs Grid**: 2x3/3x2 responsive grid with icons for display, processor, RAM, storage, camera, battery
- **Full Specifications**: Uses SpecTable component when detailed specs exist; falls back to quickSpecs list
- **AI Review**: Glass card with review text, pros (green checkmarks) and cons (red X) in side-by-side columns, AI disclaimer
- **Price Comparison**: Store cards with "Check Price" affiliate links (target="_blank", rel="nofollow")
- **Related Products**: 4 ProductCards (size="sm") sorted by same brand + same category relevance

### Search/Catalog Page (`src/pages/search.astro`)
- Loads all 1412 products with client-side serialized data
- **Filter sidebar**: Category checkboxes with counts, searchable brand list, price range inputs, star rating selector, clear-all button
- **Results grid**: Responsive 2/3/4 column grid with sort dropdown (popularity, rating, price, name, newest)
- **Client-side JS**: FlexSearch for text search, debounced input, URL param sync via `history.replaceState`, empty state handling
- **Mobile**: Filter toggle button shows/hides sidebar
- All links use `/phonehub` base path
